		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.phpbb.com/phpBB/viewtopic.php?t=427852">http://www.phpbb.com/phpBB/viewtopic.php?t=427852</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />There's a whole bunch of mods in that list - I would recommend the following to clear things up here:
<br />
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.phpbb.com/phpBB/viewtopic.php?t=266787">http://www.phpbb.com/phpBB/viewtopic.php?t=266787</a><!-- m --> - show CAPTCHA for guest posting
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.phpbb.com/phpBB/viewtopic.php?t=373695">http://www.phpbb.com/phpBB/viewtopic.php?t=373695</a><!-- m --> - don't show website/signature inputs during registration; bots will fill them in anyways (with spam URLs) and will get automatically banned
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.phpbb.com/phpBB/viewtopic.php?t=262393">http://www.phpbb.com/phpBB/viewtopic.php?t=262393</a><!-- m --> - don't show 0-post users in the member list (to hide existing spammers which register solely to list their websites)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


